{"tid":503330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前度對你嚟講算係啲咩？","createTime":"2017-12-18T17:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T18:37:46.000Z","uid":154126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef417a4f8e15cf27c2e02aba1fd73ec0780954b5","tid":503330,"uid":154126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"1）無法取代的人<br />\n2）完美情人<br />\n3）太理想配唔起<br />\n4）初戀<br />\n5）賤人<br />\n6）仆街仔/女<br />\n7）自己講⋯<br />\n<br />\n如果你同前度拍左兩年幾，現任拍左幾個月，而你發現最愛始終係前度，個心始終有佢放唔低，你會回頭嗎？<br />\n<br />\n大前題 前度個心仲有你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而係你飛人先"},{"pid":"30b24018e09c3bc704a555ba4017bd4afd09db6e","tid":503330,"uid":39650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"1. 好馬不吃回頭草。回頭即係以前所有問題已經唔係問題，可以結婚<br />\n2. 學識同前度做朋友，應該係最好既學之一"},{"pid":"3d04eb9620db1af8f5d5acb1c2c33ab135f74190","tid":503330,"uid":154126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 好馬不吃回頭草。回頭即係以前所有問題已經唔係問題，可以結婚<br />\n2. 學識同前度做朋友，應該係最好既學之一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n回頭即係以前所有問題已經唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全無諗過呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a6588d593dc8965a90274765afa2f183d88be5","tid":503330,"uid":79143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾！所有ex都係垃圾!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d921ca8873671ccf173eb9944b3a720ff3c4a78","tid":503330,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:38:53.000Z","msg":"洩慾玩具"},{"pid":"70869e492ea3433fbf5753bfb543d757fb62fba2","tid":503330,"uid":23898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T17:41:51.000Z","msg":"一個遇到個仆街仔既好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"